name: SKANError.Code
desc: Constants that indicate the type of error for an ad network attribution operation.

items.name: case adNetworkIdMissing
items.desc: The ad network identifier in the ad impression doesn’t match the value in the information property list.

items.name: case impressionMissingRequiredValue
items.desc: A required value is missing from a view-through ad impression.

items.name: case impressionNotFound
items.desc: The system can’t find the ad impression.

items.name: case invalidAdvertisedAppId
items.desc: The App Store ID of the advertised app is invalid.

items.name: case invalidCampaignId
items.desc: The campaign identifier that you provided is invalid.

items.name: case invalidSourceAppId
items.desc: The App Store ID of the app displaying the ad is invalid.

items.name: case invalidVersion
items.desc: The SKAdNetwork version number is invalid.

items.name: case mismatchedSourceAppId
items.desc: The source app identifier in the ad impression doesn’t match the app identifier in the source app.

items.name: case unsupported
items.desc: Your app attempted to use functionality that isn’t supported in the specified version.
